			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The only place that the afk trick might work for faction is the entrance to Nurga.
<br />

<br />
There is a single roamer that pops and runs back and forth from the entrance every 6-10 minutes or so. He will aggro regardless of level.  Mob's level is maybe 30s, hits for 50-75.  With regen 3 and phantom line regen, you could go afk for a while with a pet up and the pet will demolish the mob after it attacks.  Then easily regen up what was lost.
<br />

<br />
Any pet would work, besides 50+ fire.  The mob will run early if you are a much higher level, so maybe earth to keep him in place or water to kill quick.
<br />

<br />
If you have elemental empathy, you could keep the pet with burnout3 for 1 1/2 hours, which is also a boon.  You would lose out on any salts or skins that drop.  Risk is minimal since the mobs are so weak.  Even if all 5 from the cave entrance aggro you, if you have over 2k hp, you will live through it while the pet destroys them.
<br />

<br />
Just a thought.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
