				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">There is a tunnel system in Frontier Mountains that is teeming with very very low level goblins that drop salts, skins, and the old nurga/droga drops from the named.
<br />

<br />
Go there and clean up, saving all your drops. 
<br />

<br />
Took me about 4 hours of this to go from scowling to dubious with handing in all the salts and skins.
<br />

